# 2020–21 NCAA Division I women's ice hockey rankings

Two polls make up the '''2020–21 NCAA Division I women's ice hockey rankings', the USCHO.com poll and the USA Today/USA Hockey Magazine poll. As the 2020–21 season progresses, rankings are updated weekly.
